description:
It`s finally Sasatsu`s turn to take a shot at the couples photo contest. She does the best she can to act the part, but Tadakusa issues constant criticism. Then Tadakusa challenges Sasatsu to a quiz contest... and the losing duo has to address each other using nicknames. Which team will win? Either way, the Port of Nagoya Public Aquarium`s Night Aquarium sure is pretty...
Source: crunchyroll
